"signal_description": "The SIGNAL query is calculating the sum of the column 'PO Item Net Order Value in USD' from the table 'defaultview-57'. However, it is not summing up all the values in the column. It is only considering the rows where the 'Last GR Creation Date', when truncated to the day, is greater than the 'PO Item Last Requested Delivery Date' and where the 'PO Item Delivery Completed' is marked as 'Yes'. In simpler terms, it is summing up the net order value in USD for all completed delivery items where the last goods receipt creation date is later than the last requested delivery date."
